Map {
  User Story {
    Display Unsupported Orders: As a pharmacist, I want to be able to view all orders that are not supported by the pharmacy application so that I can take appropriate action.
    Select Travel Time: As a customer, I want to be able to select a travel time for my order so that I can receive my medication in a timely manner.
    Manage Inventory: As a pharmacist, I want to be able to manage the inventory of medications in the pharmacy so that I can ensure that customers have access to the medications they need.
    Track Orders: As a customer, I want to be able to track my orders so that I can know when my medication will arrive.
    Receive Notifications: As a customer, I want to be able to receive notifications when my order is ready for pickup or delivery so that I can plan accordingly.
    Generate Reports: As a pharmacist, I want to be able to generate reports on orders and inventory so that I can better manage the pharmacy.
  }
  User Interface {
    Display Unsupported Orders: As a pharmacist, I want to be able to view all orders that are not supported by the pharmacy application in an easy to read format so that I can take appropriate action.
    Select Travel Time: As a customer, I want to be able to select a travel time for my order in an intuitive way so that I can receive my medication in a timely manner.
    Manage Inventory: As a pharmacist, I want to be able to manage the inventory of medications in the pharmacy in an easy to use interface so that I can ensure that customers have access to the medications they need.
    Track Orders: As a customer, I want to be able to track my orders in an easy to use interface so that I can know when my medication will arrive.
    Receive Notifications: As a customer, I want to be able to receive notifications when my order is ready for pickup or delivery in an easy to read format so that I can plan accordingly.
    Generate Reports: As a pharmacist, I want to be able to generate reports on orders and inventory in an easy to use interface so that I can better manage the pharmacy.
  }
  Security {
    Secure Login: As a customer, I want to be able to securely log in to the pharmacy application so that my personal information is protected.
    Data Encryption: As a customer, I want to be sure that my personal data is encrypted when stored in the pharmacy application so that it is secure.
    Secure Payments: As a customer, I want to be able to make secure payments for my orders so that my financial information is protected.
  }
}
